        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-theme-500 mb-3">Full Home Redesign</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Complete transformation of your living spaces with thoughtful layouts, curated furnishings, and cohesive design.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li>• Complete space planning</li>
          <li>• Furniture selection & procurement</li>
          <li>• Color palette development</li>
          <li>• Lighting design</li>
          <li>• Art & accessory styling</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 mb-5 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-theme-500 mb-3">Room Makeover</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Focus on a single room to maximize impact. Perfect for updating your living room, bedroom, or kitchen.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li>• Space assessment</li>
          <li>• Furniture layout optimization</li>
          <li>• Color consultation</li>
          <li>• Decor selection</li>
          <li>• Budget planning</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 mb-5 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
