        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-theme-500 mb-3">Color & Styling</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Color consultations, art arrangement, and finishing touches to bring your space to life.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li>• Color palette creation</li>
          <li>• Paint selection</li>
          <li>• Art arrangement</li>
          <li>• Accessory styling</li>
          <li>• Finish selections</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
